           AFFILIATES, OFFICERS, EMPLOYEES, SUCCESSORS AND/OR ASSIGNS WILL BE LIABLE TO YOU FOR
           ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, SPECIAL, EXEMPLARY, INCIDENTAL, PUNITIVE, AND/OR CONSEQUENTIAL
           DAMAGE OF ANY KIND, IN CONTRACT, TORT OR OTHERWISE, IN CONNECTION WITH THE USE OF THE
